\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {3.2}{\ignorespaces The dashboard hosted inside an IntelliJ JCEF window. The trajectory chart (centre) plots the user's process score over the session's $37$ checkpoints, with the synthesised alternative trajectory overlaid as a dashed comparison line and divergence-point flags marked along the path. The left rail lists each per-state cleanliness signal with its session-level sparkline; the right rail shows the per-checkpoint detail panel for the currently selected refactoring (a \texttt  {Rename Attribute}), including the divergence point it produced, the IDE-event annotation, and the diff of the underlying file. The bottom strip summarises the session's highest-impact takeaway (left) and the per-metric delta across the selected step (right).}}{35}{figure.caption.38}\protected@file@percent }
